<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 00:33:05 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>是时候废除以色列政府无数多余的部门了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-27/ty-article/time-to-scrap-the-israeli-governments-countless-redundant-ministries/0000018c-0d5a-ddff-a3bc-bdfebaae0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 00:07:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-27/ty-article/time-to-scrap-the-israeli-governments-countless-redundant-ministries/0000018c-0d5a-ddff-a3bc-bdfebaae0000</guid></item><item><title>针对以色列德鲁兹公民的特别法律？不，谢谢</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/a-special-law-for-israels-druze-citizens-no-thanks/0000018c-0cfb-d65f-a7dd-fcff89a40000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sun, 26 Nov 2023 23:08:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/a-special-law-for-israels-druze-citizens-no-thanks/0000018c-0cfb-d65f-a7dd-fcff89a40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列试图阻止巴勒斯坦囚犯获释的庆祝活动揭示了战争的真正目的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/israels-bid-to-stop-celebration-of-prisoners-release-reveals-real-aim-of-war/0000018c-0cfb-d2ae-afcf-3dfb8abb0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sun, 26 Nov 2023 22:02:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-27/ty-article/.premium/israels-bid-to-stop-celebration-of-prisoners-release-reveals-real-aim-of-war/0000018c-0cfb-d2ae-afcf-3dfb8abb0000</guid></item><item><title>对于以色列人来说，哈马斯人质的释放是每晚必要的心理折磨</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-26/ty-article/.premium/for-israelis-the-hamas-hostage-releases-are-a-necessary-nightly-psychological-torture/0000018c-0cae-ddff-a3bc-bcee1a990000</link><description>哈马斯领导人伊赫·辛瓦尔不想将犹太婴儿和母亲劫持为人质。他想杀了他们。但以色列人仍然对哈马斯从家园中夺走的俘虏感到集体内疚</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 Nov 2023 21:20:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-26/ty-article/.premium/for-israelis-the-hamas-hostage-releases-are-a-necessary-nightly-psychological-torture/0000018c-0cae-ddff-a3bc-bcee1a990000</guid></item><item><title>对于拜登来说，释放四岁人质阿维盖尔始终是个人的事</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-26/ty-article/.premium/for-biden-freeing-four-year-old-hostage-avigail-mor-idan-was-always-personal/0000018c-0d63-d2ae-afcf-3df305820000</link><description>一位美国政府高级官员表示，自危机爆发以来，拜登总统一直关注美国人质问题，并补充说，“我们无法确认十名人质中许多人的下落或状况”。</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 Nov 2023 21:20:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-26/ty-article/.premium/for-biden-freeing-four-year-old-hostage-avigail-mor-idan-was-always-personal/0000018c-0d63-d2ae-afcf-3df305820000</guid></item><item><title>由于以色列和加沙战争引发的伊斯兰恐惧症加剧，三名巴勒斯坦学生在佛蒙特州伯灵顿遭到枪击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-26/ty-article/.premium/three-palestinian-students-shot-in-burlington-vermont-amid-spiking-islamphobia/0000018c-0d4e-ddff-a3bc-bdeeb2e40000</link><description>伯灵顿警察局长乔恩·穆拉德 (Jon Murad) 表示：“在这个紧张的时刻，任何人在看到这起事件时都会怀疑这可能是一起出于仇恨动机的犯罪。”</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 Nov 2023 20:53:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-26/ty-article/.premium/three-palestinian-students-shot-in-burlington-vermont-amid-spiking-islamphobia/0000018c-0d4e-ddff-a3bc-bdeeb2e40000</guid></item><item><title>美国希望以色列和哈马斯四天的暂停能够延长至周一之后，以确保更多人质安全</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-26/ty-article/.premium/u-s-hopes-israel-hamas-four-day-pause-can-be-extended-past-monday-to-secure-more-hostages/0000018c-0d34-d2ae-afcf-3df67c510000</link><description>国家安全顾问杰克·沙利文表示，以色列“准备好继续暂停战斗，哈马斯每天都会额外释放 10 名人质”</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 Nov 2023 20:28:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-26/ty-article/.premium/u-s-hopes-israel-hamas-four-day-pause-can-be-extended-past-monday-to-secure-more-hostages/0000018c-0d34-d2ae-afcf-3df67c510000</guid></item><item><title>别再为哈马斯的“人性”鼓掌了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-26/ty-article/.highlight/stop-applauding-hamas-for-its-humanity/0000018c-0d33-ddff-a3bc-bdf7cc6a0000</link><description>我们必须承认，哈马斯枪手在杀害其家人（有时是在他们眼前）后在镜头前与俘虏击掌，这为人性设置了很低的门槛</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 Nov 2023 20:15:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-26/ty-article/.highlight/stop-applauding-hamas-for-its-humanity/0000018c-0d33-ddff-a3bc-bdf7cc6a0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯周六释放 39 名巴勒斯坦囚犯，其中 8 人被判谋杀未遂罪</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-26/ty-article/.premium/8-of-the-39-palestinian-prisoners-released-in-hamas-deal-convicted-of-attempted-murder/0000018c-0ce4-d2ae-afcf-3df66a2a0000</link><description>作为从以色列监狱释放 39 名巴勒斯坦妇女和儿童的交换条件，哈马斯从加沙释放了 13 名被囚禁的以色列妇女和儿童</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 Nov 2023 19:23:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-26/ty-article/.premium/8-of-the-39-palestinian-prisoners-released-in-hamas-deal-convicted-of-attempted-murder/0000018c-0ce4-d2ae-afcf-3df66a2a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列北部基布兹居民阻止巴勒斯坦人收获橄榄</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-26/ty-article/.premium/northern-israeli-kibbutz-residents-prevent-palestinians-from-harvesting-their-olives/0000018c-0cc4-ddff-a3bc-bce4f31b0000</link><description>多年来，巴勒斯坦人一直被允许通过边境收获橄榄。今年，附近基布兹的居民举行抗议活动，阻止他们这样做。尽管最初授予巴勒斯坦人进入权，但以色列军队拒绝驱散抗议者</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 Nov 2023 18:31:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-26/ty-article/.premium/northern-israeli-kibbutz-residents-prevent-palestinians-from-harvesting-their-olives/0000018c-0cc4-ddff-a3bc-bce4f31b0000</guid></item><item><title>叙利亚称以色列袭击导致大马士革机场停止服务</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-11-26/ty-article/syria-says-israeli-strike-puts-damascus-airport-out-of-service/0000018c-0ca4-d679-abdc-9ebcc0db0000</link><description>据报道，以色列多年来一直对其所谓的叙利亚境内与伊朗有关的目标进行袭击，而美国最近也证实，以色列针对叙利亚境内的伊斯兰革命卫队设施进行了袭击，以回应针对美国人员的袭击</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 Nov 2023 18:09:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-11-26/ty-article/syria-says-israeli-strike-puts-damascus-airport-out-of-service/0000018c-0ca4-d679-abdc-9ebcc0db0000</guid></item><item><title>人权观察称阿赫利医院爆炸可能由巴勒斯坦火箭造成</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-26/ty-article/.premium/al-ahli-hospital-explosion-likely-caused-by-palestinian-rocket-human-rights-watch-says/0000018c-0c96-d65f-a7dd-fcd7c1cc0000</link><description>该事件的最初报道引用了哈马斯的说法，即以色列轰炸了该医院，并在爆炸中造成 500 人死亡——人权观察现在表示这两种说法不太可能是正确的</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 Nov 2023 17:30:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-26/ty-article/.premium/al-ahli-hospital-explosion-likely-caused-by-palestinian-rocket-human-rights-watch-says/0000018c-0c96-d65f-a7dd-fcd7c1cc0000</guid></item><item><title>油轮在也门海岸被劫持，这是自加沙战争开始以来第三次针对与以色列有关的船只的袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-26/ty-article/israeli-linked-tanker-hijacked-off-coast-of-yemen/0000018c-0be4-d679-abdc-9ffc65b10000</link><description>不到一周前，也门胡塞叛军劫持了一艘货船，该货船部分归以色列商人旗下的一家公司所有。</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 Nov 2023 16:01:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-26/ty-article/israeli-linked-tanker-hijacked-off-coast-of-yemen/0000018c-0be4-d679-abdc-9ffc65b10000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日，全女性以色列坦克兵在 17 个小时的战斗中杀死了 50 名恐怖分子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-26/ty-article/all-woman-israeli-tank-crews-killed-50-terrorists-over-17-hours-of-combat-on-october-7/0000018c-0bec-d65f-a7dd-fbfff6dd0000</link><description>据以色列国防军称，这些坦克乘员由20岁出头的年轻女性组成，是第一批投入战斗的西方女装甲兵。</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 Nov 2023 15:20:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-26/ty-article/all-woman-israeli-tank-crews-killed-50-terrorists-over-17-hours-of-combat-on-october-7/0000018c-0bec-d65f-a7dd-fbfff6dd0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人遭到屠杀和绑架？阿拉伯媒体上没有</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israelis-massacred-and-abducted-not-in-the-arab-media/0000018c-0b89-de3d-af9e-0bdfaf9c0000</link><description>相反，哈马斯的袭击在很大程度上被描述为合法的抵抗行为，尽管并非每个国家的媒体都将加沙的恐怖组织与巴勒斯坦人民等同起来</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 Nov 2023 14:26:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israelis-massacred-and-abducted-not-in-the-arab-media/0000018c-0b89-de3d-af9e-0bdfaf9c0000</guid></item><item><title>美国大学校园的哈马斯与以色列辩论并未以毒性为主导</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-26/ty-article-opinion/.premium/progressive-trolls-dont-rule-the-israel-hamas-war-debate-on-u-s-campuses/0000018c-0b5d-dca2-a9fd-6fdf526f0000</link><description>作为在美国大学工作的犹太裔以色列学者，我们知道校园中两极分化和背叛的形象被夸大了。我们遇到的大多数学生和同事都充满好奇和开放的态度，想了解更多有关以色列-哈马斯战争的信息</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 Nov 2023 13:31:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-26/ty-article-opinion/.premium/progressive-trolls-dont-rule-the-israel-hamas-war-debate-on-u-s-campuses/0000018c-0b5d-dca2-a9fd-6fdf526f0000</guid></item><item><title>纽约市一名参加亲以色列集会的老师因学生骚乱而躲在上锁的房间里</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-26/ty-article/n-y-c-mayor-slams-incident-that-saw-teacher-who-attended-israel-rally-hide-in-locked-room/0000018c-0bad-ddff-a3bc-bbed08310000</link><description>据《纽约邮报》报道，学生们发现 Facebook 帖子显示该老师曾参加集会，试图闯入她的教室，迫使她被警察疏散。市长埃里克·亚当斯表示，这一事件是“反犹太主义的卑鄙表现”</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 Nov 2023 13:24:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-26/ty-article/n-y-c-mayor-slams-incident-that-saw-teacher-who-attended-israel-rally-hide-in-locked-room/0000018c-0bad-ddff-a3bc-bbed08310000</guid></item><item><title>“这不是我们的战斗”：斯雷布雷尼察种族灭绝纪念碑馆长因以色列与哈马斯的战争反应而受到攻击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/director-of-srebrenica-genocide-memorial-targeted-over-october-7-response/0000018c-0b72-de3d-af9e-0bf7d0400000</link><description>埃米尔·苏尔贾吉奇本人也是斯雷布雷尼察幸存者，他因拒绝评论以色列与哈马斯的战争而受到批评，并宣称他不会“无论哈马斯的议程如何改变”而牺牲自己组织的工作。</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 Nov 2023 13:06:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/director-of-srebrenica-genocide-memorial-targeted-over-october-7-response/0000018c-0b72-de3d-af9e-0bf7d0400000</guid></item><item><title>以色列外长称爱尔兰总理在推特发布人质获释后将恐怖活动合法化</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-26/ty-article/.premium/israeli-foreign-minister-says-irish-pm-legitimizing-terror-after-tweet-about-freed-hostage/0000018c-0b22-d99b-a7ee-1fb6f1290000</link><description>总理利奥·瓦拉德卡 (Leo Varadkar) 的推文称艾米丽·汉德 (Emily Hand) 是“迷失”而不是被绑架，社交媒体用户指出，他暗指《新约》，他的完整回应将她描述为人质</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 Nov 2023 12:28:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-26/ty-article/.premium/israeli-foreign-minister-says-irish-pm-legitimizing-terror-after-tweet-about-freed-hostage/0000018c-0b22-d99b-a7ee-1fb6f1290000</guid></item><item><title>由于无法逃离哈马斯的火箭弹，贝都因人选择谈论他们的恐惧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/unable-to-escape-hamas-rockets-bedouin-choose-to-talk-about-their-fears/0000018c-0b57-d4d0-addf-4fff17880000</link><description>迄今为止，以色列贝都因社区已有 19 名成员在战争中丧生，其中包括 6 名儿童。阿拉伯心理学家和社会工作者的热线已成为他们中许多人安慰和支持的最佳资源</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 Nov 2023 11:57:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-26/ty-article-magazine/.premium/unable-to-escape-hamas-rockets-bedouin-choose-to-talk-about-their-fears/0000018c-0b57-d4d0-addf-4fff17880000</guid></item></channel></rss>